{"tid":2078479,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍機闖台外海 騷擾美軍機","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T05:31:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8ef89e6b5de6ea21a354f6aee547013078fdd8","tid":2078479,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/QZ4XBUHEN5AT4QKUPTZJSJQT4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FQZ4XBUHEN5AT4QKUPTZJSJQT4A%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=231899c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FQZ4XBUHEN5AT4QKUPTZJSJQT4A%2F&h=2ab11380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/QZ4XBUHEN5AT4QKUPTZJSJQT4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n解放軍機闖台外海 騷擾美軍機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dEYeT2ipx7UjZU1XicOw62QMy00=/190x106/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V4IPBQEEHHNZMAWCTRV7THV5IE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdEYeT2ipx7UjZU1XicOw62QMy00%3D%2F190x106%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV4IPBQEEHHNZMAWCTRV7THV5IE.jpg&h=db7880f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台軍戰機（左）早前監視侵台解放軍戰機。<br />\n<br />\n台媒引述航空迷消息指，大陸解放軍戰機不僅接近台灣西南角的防空識別區，昨日甚至穿越台灣與菲律賓之間的巴士海峽，直接到台灣防空識別區東南方外空域（台灣外島蘭嶼附近），逼近正在加油的美軍P-3C反潛機及KC-135加油機，美軍以空中示警的方式，要求解放軍戰機不要逼近。台空軍退休將領指出，解放軍戰機以相當罕見的方式接近加油機，對正在進行加油的美軍戰機產生威脅。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中華戰略學會研究員張競表示，解放軍戰機大膽飛越巴士海峽，逼近<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n上，解放軍都還不是美軍的對手。台軍表示，由於事發地點在台灣防空識別區外，台灣國防部不便評論。美國太平洋空軍司令布朗（Charles Q. Brown Jr.）昨表示，對解放軍近期繁密在南海與台海行動感到憂心，揚言美軍將加強威嚇力，履行對印太盟友的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華閉門會議斥美軍援台<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國國務卿蓬佩奧17日與中共中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\nF-16系列戰機表達不滿，但蓬佩奧反駁：「對台軍售完全適當，與美國歷任政府作法一致」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"eb22bc08379b29b162078d5fe445fe87f6d3f7ca","tid":2078479,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"你地打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e0d9edd4cc9a041fd2fc393e2bc2928956643c","tid":2078479,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"摺被狗連正面打既勇氣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}